            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Maybe you could at a note/warning that his command will throw away the commit &lt;b&gt;and the changes in the working directory&lt;/b&gt; without asking any further.&lt;/span&gt;

